  _playCardButton: {fileID: 5759974893741796741}
  _perfectTarget: {fileID: 7045099373454778651, guid: 94ebcab5d3d71274d8fd94c7d4ebe9e4, type: 3}
  _story: "As an External Technical Producer on Google Stadia, Neil supported multiple
    3rd party developers as they ported their games to Linux and Vulkan, as per the
    Stadia platform requirements. Working closely with 3rd party Lead Programmers
    and Producers, Neil tracked development velocity and identified production risks.\n\nBy
    flagging issues early, Neil was able to loop in Google Technical Solutions Engineers
    to do deep dives on blocking issues before they impacted delivery deadlines.
    \n\nBonus: Schedule an inerview with Neil and he may tell you about the time
    he inherited a team that wasn't as transparent as it could have been... and how
    he helped that team recover from near complete disaster."
